title: Budget Airline Exec Calls Out Trump Enabler Elon Musk
description:
The budget airline Ryanair has turned the tables on Tesla CEO Elon Musk, leveraging an online feud over Musk's Skylink service for free publicity.

The post Budget Airline Exec Calls Out Trump Enabler Elon Musk appeared first on CleanTechnica.
